version_description: My version is different because mine is taken from Dave Grohl playing it without the rest of the band.  Other tabs put the third verse with the chords for the chorus which were also wrong.  All in all I watched Dave Grohl play it in a video and he makes it so much more simple than people are trying to make it.
My hero is an amazing song this version I put together from watching Dave Grohl play it live so I think it is accurate Enjoy playing. https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=nGa1syRUbRQ.
Added chords to all lyric, made correction on chorus repetitions, much easier to read for beginners,.
This is the tab of the entire song including a tab for the intro, solo and outro. Also, this tab requires capo on the 2nd fret throughout.
No capo, all riffs changed to chords. Based on studio version.
Correct Chords and Tab of riff all in one.
